{"text": "Starbucks Corporation, doing business as Starbucks Coffee, is an American global coffee company and coffeehouse chain based in Seattle, Washington. Starbucks is the largest coffeehouse company in the world ahead of UK rival Costa Coffee, with 21,536 stores in 64 countries and territories, including 12,218 in the United States, 1,716 in China, 1,330 in Canada, 1,079 in Japan and 808 in the United Kingdom.Starbucks locations serve hot and cold beverages, whole-bean coffee, microground instant coff..", "title": "Starbucks - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia"}
